DCI detectives on Wednesday made an arrest of a man impersonating a
KDF officer. Erick Otieno Atanga is accused of presenting himself as Colonel Kiprotich
of the Department of Defense. He is also accused of selling fake tenders to unsuspecting Kenyans, defrauding them of lots of cash. The DCI said Atanga will be charged with obtaining money by false pretenses. He will be arraigned today. Click here for the latest political news